;&quot;&gt;Temperature control&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;into a single enclosure,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;converting electrical energy into laser light energy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Principle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Utilizing the principle of selective absorption at wavelengths of 980nm and 1470nm,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;it is widely used in soft tissue surgery, vascular treatment, tissue ablation, and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;skin disease treatment, providing advanced solutions for medical professionals worldwide.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;WEB_DOMAIN_XUNRUICMS_URL/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202511/1763695573a4a0d0.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Principle of 980nm-1470nm-laser-diode&quot; alt=&quot;Principle of 980nm-1470nm-laser-diode&quot; width=&quot;578&quot; height=&quot;325&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-fa